;Mail Account Setup Wizard
Amarag n twila n umiḍan imayl


;Prior to this feature you had to know your IMAP, SMTP, and SSL/TLS settings. Now all you need to provide is your name, email address, and password and the email account set up wizardry will check our database and find the email settings for you.
Send ad d-ban tmahilt-agi, yessefk ad tissineḍ iɣewwaṛen IMAP, SMTP, SSL/TLS n imḍanen inek. Tura mudd kan isem-ik, tansa yinek n yimayl akked wawal uffir, sakin amarag amaynut ad yexdem ayen nniden s unadi di taffa n isefka n iɣewwaṛen n usaǧǧaw inek n yimayl.


;One-click Address Book
Imedlis n tenṣa ɣef afus


;One-click Address Book is a quick and easy way to add people to your address book. Add people by simply clicking on the star icon in the message you receive. Two clicks and you can add more details like a photo, birthday, and other contact information.
Imedlis n tensa ɣef afus d allal arurad, fessusen akken ad ternud imdanen ar imedlis n tensa. Rnu anermis s usiti ɣef uqerru n yizen i d-remseḍ. Ma tsiteḍ snat n tikal tzemreḍ ad ternud ugar n telɣut am tewlaft, azemz n tlalit, d wayen nniḍen.


;Attachment Reminder
Asmekti n imeddayen


;The attachment reminder looks for the word attachment (and other words like file types) in the body of your message and reminds you to add an attachment before hitting send.
Anagraw n ulɣu ad yesleḍ akken ad inadi awalen am amedday, isemli, afaylu (neɣ ismawen n isiɣzaf n ifuyla) udiɣ ak-id-immekti ad tsedduḍ isemli ma yella tettuḍ.


;Tabs
Iccaren


;If you like Firefox’s tabbed browsing, you’re going to love tabbed email. Tabbed email lets you load emails in separate tabs so you can quickly jump between them. Perhaps you’re responding to an email and need to refer back to an earlier email. Tabbed email lets you keep multiple emails open for easy reference.
Ma tḥemleḍ tunigin s yiccaren n Firefox, ad tiḥmileḍ iccaren n Thunderbird. Asnas n yeznan s yiccaren n Thunderbird ak-yeǧǧ ad d-saliḍ iznan inek yal yiwen deg iccer akken ad tizmireḍ  ad tedduḍ seg iwen ar wayeḍ s zreb. Aqlak tettarraḍ i yizen daɣen tesriḍ ad twaliḍ izen nniḍen aqbuṛ? Asnas n yeznan  s yiccaren ak-yeǧǧ ad tḥ€rzeḍ deqs n yiccaren ldin deg iwen n usfaylu akken ad yifsus useqdec.


;Double-clicking or hitting enter on a mail message will now open that message in a new tab window. Right-clicking on messages or folders will open them in a tab in the background.
Ticki tsiteḍ snat n tikal ɣef yizen neɣ tsendeḍ ɣef tqeffalt Kcem ticki izen yettwafren, izen ad d-yeldi deg iccer amaynut. Yiwen n usiti ayeffus ɣef yeznan neɣ ikaramen ad -yeldi deg iccer deg ugilal.


;When quitting Thunderbird, visible tabs will be saved and will be restored when you open Thunderbird the next time. There is also a Tab menu on the Tab toolbar to help you switch between Tabs.
Ticki tmedleḍ Thunderbird, iccaren d-ibanen ad ttwakelsen sakin ad d-uɣalen di tnekra n Thunderbird. Yella wumuɣ amaynut Iccer deg ufeggag n yiccaren akken ak-d-imudd afus ticki tettedduḍ seg iccer ara wayeḍ.


;Quick Filter Toolbar
Afeggag n ifecka n imzizdig arurad


;The Quick Filter Toolbar lets you filter your email faster. Start typing in words in the Quick Filter search box and the results are displayed instantly. Or you can filter your email by New Messages, Tags, and people in your Address Book. You can also "Pin" or save a Filter and use it across multiple folders.
Afeggag n ifecka n imzizgid arurad ak-yeǧǧ ad tezizdgeḍ iznan inek s zreb. Sekcem di tazwara awalen deg ufeggag n unadiarurad sakin igmaḍ ad d-banen imiren kan. Tzemreḍ daɣen ad tezizdgeḍ s Iznan imaynuten, Tibzimin, akked yemdanen n imedlis inek n tensa. Tzemreḍ daɣen ad sekelseḍ imzizdig akked ad tesqedceḍ tikelt nniḍen.


;Search
Nadi


;The search interface in Thunderbird contains filtering and timeline tools to pinpoint the exact email you’re looking for. Thunderbird also indexes all of your emails to help you search even faster. Your search results are displayed in a tab so you can easily switch back and forth to your search results and other email.
Agrudem n unadi n Thunderbird yegber ifecka n uzizdeg akked usmizzwer askudan akked ad d-yaf izen tettnadiḍ. Thunderbird irennu amatar i yeznan inek akken ak-d-imudd afus deg unadi n s zreb. Igmaḍ inek n unadi ad d-ttwaseknen deg iccer amaynut akken ad tizmireḍ ad ten-twaliḍ udiɣ ad d-uɣaleḍ  s zreb ar igmaḍ n unadi.


;Message Archive
Aḥraz n yizen


;If you think you’re going to need an email in the future but want it out of your inbox without deleting it, archive it! Archiving helps you manage your inbox and put your email into the archive folder system.
Ma tɣileḍ tesriḍ aḥraz n yizen ur tebɣiḍ ara ad yili di tebwaṭ inek n urmes war ma tekkseṭ, ḥerz-it! Aḥraz ak-dimudd afus deg usefrek n tebwaṭ inek n yeznan udiɣ ad yawi izen ar unagraw amaynut n ikaramen n uḥraz.


;Selecting the Archive button or hitting the ‘A’ key will archive your email.
Akken ad tḥerzeḍ izen, Fren taqeffalt ḥrez neɣ tekki ɣef tqeffalt ‘A’ .


;Activity Manager
Amsefrak n urmud


;The Activity Manager records all the interactions between Thunderbird and your email provider in one place. There’s no more guess work. You only have to look in one place to see everything that’s happening with your email.
Amsefrak n urmud ad isekles tamyigawt gar Thunderbird akked usaǧǧaw inek n yimayl deg iwen n umḍiq. Dayen, ur tesrid ara ad tɛasseḍ iznan inek. Yiwen kan n umḍiq anda ara twaliḍ.


;Thunderbird Look & Feel
Talɣa n Thunderbird


;With Personas, lightweight "skins" allow you to change the look and feel of Thunderbird in an instant. Hundreds of skins are available from the latest movies, famous landmarks, and Japanese tattoos. You can also choose from several Themes that dress up all the different icons in Thunderbird.
S Personas, isental ifessasen ak-eǧǧen ad tesnifleḍ udem n Thunderbird s zreb. Deqs n isental Parsonas i yellan seg isura ineggura, timeẓriyin yettwasnen neɣ ticraḍ tijapuniyin. Tzemreḍ daɣen ad tferneḍ isental nniḍen akken ad tesnifleḍ tigitin n Thunderbird.


;Smart Folders
Ikaramen iḥeṛcen


;Smart Folders help you manage multiple email accounts by combining special folders like your Inbox, Sent, or Archive folder. Instead of going to the Inbox for each of your mail accounts, you can see all of your incoming email in one Inbox folder.
Ikaramen iḥ€rcen sifsusen asefrek n imiḍanen n yimayl s tuddsa n ikaramen imeẓliyen am tebwaḍin n tuzna d urmas, neɣ ikaramen n uḥraz. Deg umḍiq n uwali ar yal tabwaṭ n urmas n yal amiḍan iman-is, tzemreḍ ad twaliḍ akk iznan d-ikecmen deg iwen n ukaram.


;Add-ons Manager
Amsefrak n izegrar


;Find and install add-ons directly in Thunderbird. You no longer need to visit the add-ons Web site - instead simply fire up the Add-ons Manager. Not sure which add-on is right for you? Ratings, recommendations, descriptions and pictures of the add-ons in action help you make your selection.
Nadi sakin sebded izegrar srid si Thunderbird. Ur tesrid ara ad tedduḍ ar usmel n izegrar - Senker kan amsefrak n izegrar. Ur teẓriḍ ara anwa azegrir ara tesbeddeḍ? Tizmilin, aweṣṣi, aglam akked tuṭṭfiwin n ugdil zemren ak-d-mudden afus deg ufran.


;Robust Privacy
Tabaḍnit iǧehden


;Thunderbird offers support for user privacy and remote image protection. To ensure a user’s privacy, Thunderbird automatically blocks remote images in email messages.
Thunderbird yetttḥărab ɣef tudert inek tusligt akked uselkim inek mgal askan n tugniwin ur ilaqemn ara. Akken ad neḍmen ammesten-agi, Thunderbird isewḥal s wudem awurman tugniwin tinmeggagin yellan deg iznan.


;Phishing Protection
Ammesten mgal tandit


;Thunderbird protects you from email scams which try to trick users into handing over personal and confidential information by indicating when a message is a potential phishing attempt. As a second line of defense, Thunderbird warns you when you click on a link which appears to be taking you to a different Web site than the one indicated by the URL in the message.
Thunderbird ak-immesten mgal iskamen (iznan n tandit)  ara k-yeǧǧen ad tamneḍ am akken izen yekka-d seg wid yettwamanen akken ad awin talɣut tudmawant neɣ tabaḍnit inek neɣ ad akkren tamagit inek. Iznan-agi ttwammalen d ixeṣṣaren di Thunderbird. Thunderbird yeqqaṛ ɣur-wat ticki aseɣwen URL yellan deg izen yettawi ar usmel nniḍen yettwammlen deg izen.


;Automated Update
Aleqqem awurman


;Thunderbird’s update system checks to see if you’re running the latest version, and notifies you when a security update is available. These security updates are small (usually 200KB - 700KB), giving you only what you need and making the security update quick to download and install. The automated update system provides updates for Thunderbird on Windows, Mac OS X, and Linux in over 40 different languages.
Anagraw n uleqqem n Thunderbird  ad isenqed ma tseqdaceḍ lqem aneggaru yellan udiq ak-id-yelɣu s wudem awurman ticki yella lqem amaynut n  tɣellist. Teɣzi n ileqman-agi meẓẓiyet  (gar 200 KAṬ - 700 KAṬ). Gebren kan ayen ilaqen akken ad yerr lqem fessus i usider akked usebded. Anagraw n uleqqem awurman yettmudu-d ileqman di Windows, Mac OS X akked Linux deg ugar n 40 n tutlayin gar-asent Taqbaylit.


;Cutting Out the Junk
Ḍegger ispamen


;Thunderbird’s popular junk mail tools have been updated to stay ahead of spam. Each email you receive passes through Thunderbird’s leading-edge junk mail filters. Each time you mark messages as spam, Thunderbird "learns" and improves its filtering so you can spend more time reading the mail that matters. Thunderbird can also use your mail provider’s spam filters to keep junk mail out of your inbox.
Ifecka n tuṭṭfa n yeznan ispamen di Thunderbird ttwaleqmen akken ad izmiren ad ḥarben mgal ispamen. Yal izen id-yettwaremsen ad iɛeddi ɣef imzizdig amgal-aspam n Thunderbird. Yal tikelt i tceṛḍeḍ izen amzun d aspam, Thunderbird "ad yissin" sakin ad isnerni azizdeg ines, ayen ara kyeǧǧen ad teɣreḍ iznan inek ilaqen. Thunderbird yezmer daɣen ad iseqdec imzizdigen amgal-ispamen n usaǧǧaw inek n yimayl akken ur tettezziḍ ara ad d-remseḍ ispamen di tebwaṭ inek n urmas.


;Open Source
Aɣbalu yeldin


;At the heart of Thunderbird is an open source development process driven by thousands of passionate, experienced developers and security experts spread all over the world. Our openness and active community of experts helps to ensure our products are more secure and quickly updated, while also enabling us to take advantage of the best third party security scanning and evaluation tools to further bolster overall security.
Thunderbird yekka-d si tneflit n useɣẓan ilelli i ggan wagimen n ineflayen ifazen iḥemlen aseɣẓan, d imazzagen di tɣellist i d-yekkan seg umaḍal meṛṛa. Tamezdagnut nneɣ n imazzagend turmiṭ udiɣ teldi, tettmuddu-yaɣ-d afus akken ad neḍmen taɣlellist akked uleqqem n ifarisen-nneɣ s zreb, ayagi daɣen s ufaṛes n tegnitt n ifecka ifazen n usenqed akked usekyed n t qellist akken ad neseǧhed taɣellist tamatut.


